snippet.title: Leaked Audio Proofs Amber Heard Abused Johnny Depp
snippet.description: New Audio was obtained through the Daily Mail of a taped phone call and argument the couple had during their marriage and divorce and I wanted to discuss this because I want to really stress to all that MEN ARE VICTIMS as well these things can and do happen and I think it's important we shine a light on this  so men are not scared, shunned or silenced any longer I speak on behalf of all men I'm here to tell you I'm here with you and I believe you and you are not alone #JohnnyDepp #AmberHeard
